/*----------------------------Description of the PDF-------------------------
 * This is PDF class for Bs->J/psi Pi Pi Dalitz Plot Fit.
 * It uses 2 invariant masses to describe the amplitude.
 * For signal Amplitude we have used,
 * A(m12,m13) = equation (2) of Physical Review D 78, 072004 (2008)
 * and hence the signal PDF S(m12, m13) = a_i*exp(-i*phi)*A(m12,m13)
 * Total amplitude is based on PLB 719 (2013) 383
 *****************************************************************************/

